description: Introducing a truly stunning 3 bedroom, 3.5 bathroom Penthouse residence in the heart of Boston's Seaport District. This 3,573 square foot, custom renovated penthouse in the renowned 50 Liberty building offers the epitome of modern waterfront living. This smart penthouse includes electric shades throughout and high tech audio system which can be controlled with your phone. Situated on the uppermost floors of this exclusive development, PH2A embodies elegance and sophistication, featuring an array of amenities and stunning architectural details that make it one of the most desirable condos in Boston. Hardwood flooring runs throughout the penthouse creating an inviting warmth. The floor-to-ceiling windows that span the entirety of the living area provide breathtaking, unobstructed views of the tranquil waters of Boston Harbor, allowing residents to bask in the beauty of the city's waterfront. Unit includes 3 deeded, heated, garage parking spaces and an enormous private storage unit.
